        <inbodydescription>
<para>Send IPI CDO to PLM. Return XST_FAILURE, if failure in IPI send request.</para><para>Wait for IPI response from PLM with a default timeout of 2 seconds. If the timeout exceeds, then error is returned otherwise it returns the status of the IPI response.</para>        </inbodydescription>
